title: Add the company 'Eternal', along with its Q4FY25 r

messages.content: Add the company 'Eternal', along with its Q4FY25 report which can be found at https://b.zmtcdn.com/investor-relations/d9c290cd23764a09789769c39682276a_1746094084.pdf, also extract Revenue from operations from this file. Once you find it, cite and export it as well

I have successfully added **Eternal** to the Financial Knowledge Graph and processed its Q4FY25 report. Here is the summary of the actions performed:

### 1. Knowledge Graph Updated
- **Company Added**: 'Eternal' (ID: `companies/374`)
- **Filing Added**: Q4FY25 Report (ID: `filings/381`)
- **Metric Stored**: Revenue from operations (Value: **5,833 Crores INR**)

### 2. Metric Extraction
The "Revenue from operations" was extracted from page 15 of the provided PDF.

### 3. Visual Citation
A visual citation with the source text and value highlighted has been generated:
- **Citation Path**: `/output/citations/Eternal_Q4FY25_Revenue/page_15_citation.png`

### 4. Excel Export
The extracted data has been exported to a structured Excel report:
- **Export Path**: `/output/exports/Eternal_Q4FY25_Report.xlsx`

You can now find the data in the knowledge graph, or access the generated image and spreadsheet in the respective output directories.

args.aql_query:
FOR c IN companies
  FILTER LOWER(c.name) == LOWER(@name)
  RETURN c

INSERT {
  nse_symbol: @symbol,
  type: "Quarterly",
  period: "Q4FY25",
  pdf_url: @pdf_url
} INTO filings
RETURN NEW

cells.content: Add: Actual customer delivery charges paid in the food delivery business
Add: Gross platform fee paid in the food delivery business
Less: Platform fee paid in the food delivery business (that is already included in Revenue)
Add: Rental paid pertaining to 'Ind AS 116 leases'

footnotes.content: 1) Provision for income tax has been created on other income (primarily being treasury income) post adjustment of unabsorbed depreciation permitted under the Income Tax Act. No provision is created on business income since that is being set off against the carried forward losses from the past years.
2) There could be some totalling anomalies in the numbers displayed above due to the impact of rounding off.

paragraphs.content: Annexure B - Adjusted Revenue and Adjusted EBITDA reconciliation
The following table reconciles revenue from operations and stated loss for the period (as per Ind AS) with Adjusted Revenue and Adjusted EBITDA, respectively.
Add: Actual customer delivery charges paid in the food delivery business

1) Provision for income tax has been created on other income (primarily being treasury income) post adjustment of unabsorbed depreciation permitted under the Income Tax Act. No provision is created on business income since that is being set off against the carried forward losses from the past years.
